fields.name: Eco-Friendly Yoga Mat
fields.description:
Our Eco-Friendly Yoga Mat is the perfect companion for your yoga practice. Crafted from natural rubber, it provides superior grip and cushioning for stability and support during poses. The non-toxic, PVC-free design is both eco-friendly and safe for you and the environment. Lightweight and portable, it's easy to take with you wherever you go. Elevate your practice with our sustainable and stylish yoga mat.

Structure: Closed-cell construction
Grip Type: High grip
Dimensions: 24" x 68"
Thickness: 4 mm / 5/32 inch
Weight: 2.75 lbs.
Material: Natural rubber with microfiber suede top layer
Care: Wipe down with a damp cloth and mild soap, air dry flat
Country of Origin: Made in the USA
